<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Awfsez </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, wir schiken zu
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> disen
                                                  <expan>gegenw<ex>er</ex>tig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>antwurt<ex>er</ex></expan> disz brif, und
                                                  <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> an ewch von
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> und gemeins lands
                                                nucz und notdurft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                                                ir schiket und bestellet und
                                                  <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> söllich
                                                  <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und
                                                  <expan>kuntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> gen Holvelt
                                                gebet, damit der Jobs Peler,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> und der
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>recht<ex>er</ex></expan> gschol, gemeͣrt und
                                                  <expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sucht</expan> werde. Denn von des
                                                rechttags <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ub<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> Peler auf den
                                          <app><note><q type="date"><expan>freit<ex>ag</ex></expan> schierist vor
                                            <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> tag</q>30.10.1422</note></app>, als nehst bey
                                                uns mit ewch geredt und
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ist,
                                                  <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> und manen wir ewr
                                                  <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir bestellet
                                                und <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> fleisz also darczu
                                                tuet, daz den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die
                                                wir zu <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> rechttag
                                                gefertigt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, auf
                                                  <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag rechtes zu
                                                dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Peler
                                                  <expan>geholff<ex>en</ex></expan> und darein niht
                                                  <expan>getrag<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, als etc. Das wellen
                                                etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> xi<hi rend="sup">m</hi>
<expan>virginu<ex>m</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
